FBIS3-9295 "dreeu056_d_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 SLOVAKIA New Head of Government Office Appointed LD2203154594 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1400 GMT 22 Mar 94 LD2203154594 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1400 GMT 22 Mar 94 Language: Slovak Article Type:BFN [Text] Jan Filko, current commissioner of the Slovak Government for legislature and deputy chairman of the Legislative Council of the government, has become head of the government office. According to Deputy Prime Minister Roman Kovac, the government office was taken out of the system of other central bodies of state administration today and will fulfill only organizational and technical tasks for the needs of the government.
